通过检查可以看出，空间向量
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{\boldsymbol{v}}=\omega_{x}\boldsymbol{d}_{Ox}+\omega_{y}\boldsymbol{d}_{Oy}+\omega_{z}\boldsymbol{d}_{Oz}+v_{Ox}\boldsymbol{d}_{x}+v_{Oy}\boldsymbol{d}_{y}+v_{Oz}\boldsymbol{d}_{z}\label{eq:6}
