\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{D}_{O}$
\end_inset

是引起在
\begin_inset Formula $\mathsf{M}^{6}$
\end_inset

中与
\begin_inset Formula $Oxyz$
\end_inset

相关联的Plücker坐标系统的基，并且坐标向量
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\underline{\hat{\boldsymbol{v}}}_{O}=\left[\begin{array}{cccccc}
\omega_{x} & \omega_{y} & \omega_{z} & v_{Ox} & v_{Oy} & v_{Oz}\end{array}\right]^{\mathrm{T}}\in\mathsf{R}^{6}\label{eq:7}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

